[
    {
        "text": "♪ I'm gonna smoke me a fatty brisket ♪",
        "start": 1.028,
        "duration": 3.192
    },
    {
        "text": "- [Bobby Fame] Welcome to\nBarbecue Pit Boys dot com.",
        "start": 4.22,
        "duration": 3.08
    },
    {
        "text": "Today, we're grilling up some",
        "start": 7.3,
        "duration": 1.73
    },
    {
        "text": "smothered pork chops at the pit.",
        "start": 9.03,
        "duration": 2.47
    },
    {
        "text": "And it's real easy to do.",
        "start": 11.5,
        "duration": 2.17
    },
    {
        "text": "All right, we have to thank\nthe National Pork Board",
        "start": 13.67,
        "duration": 2.87
    },
    {
        "text": "for sponsoring this Pit Boys video.",
        "start": 16.54,
        "duration": 2.35
    },
    {
        "text": "We appreciate your support.",
        "start": 18.89,
        "duration": 1.85
    },
    {
        "text": "All right, here I have a half loin roast.",
        "start": 20.74,
        "duration": 3.25
    },
    {
        "text": "This is a pork loin roast.",
        "start": 23.99,
        "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
        "text": "And with this recipe,\nwe're gonna need some",
        "start": 26.79,
        "duration": 2.27
    },
    {
        "text": "chicken broth, some oil, some seasoning.",
        "start": 29.06,
        "duration": 3.08
    },
    {
        "text": "Here, we've got an onion.",
        "start": 32.14,
        "duration": 1.82
    },
    {
        "text": "You're gonna need a stick of butter.",
        "start": 33.96,
        "duration": 2.39
    },
    {
        "text": "You're gonna need some garlic. Oh yeah.",
        "start": 36.35,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "You're gonna need some sprigs of thyme.",
        "start": 39.08,
        "duration": 2.003
    },
    {
        "text": "Here, we've got some flour for thickening.",
        "start": 42.01,
        "duration": 2.413
    },
    {
        "text": "Here we have some paprika.",
        "start": 45.61,
        "duration": 2.39
    },
    {
        "text": "We've got some mustard.",
        "start": 48.0,
        "duration": 1.99
    },
    {
        "text": "And we've got some mushrooms.",
        "start": 49.99,
        "duration": 2.43
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 52.42,
        "duration": 1.31
    },
    {
        "text": "Let's put this together.",
        "start": 53.73,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, this is considered a\nhalf of a pork loin, right?",
        "start": 54.85,
        "duration": 4.77
    },
    {
        "text": "It's actually the blade end or rib end",
        "start": 59.62,
        "duration": 3.57
    },
    {
        "text": "and a sirloin end have been removed,",
        "start": 63.19,
        "duration": 2.25
    },
    {
        "text": "so they're calling this a roast.",
        "start": 65.44,
        "duration": 2.48
    },
    {
        "text": "And um,",
        "start": 67.92,
        "duration": 1.69
    },
    {
        "text": "just take a look at that, how lean.",
        "start": 69.61,
        "duration": 2.273
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, we got ours at Walmart.",
        "start": 73.44,
        "duration": 1.81
    },
    {
        "text": "You definitely gotta check it out.",
        "start": 75.25,
        "duration": 2.26
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, to make chops like this,",
        "start": 77.51,
        "duration": 2.663
    },
    {
        "text": "it'll cost you about half",
        "start": 81.01,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "of what a butcher would charge you, right.",
        "start": 83.01,
        "duration": 2.41
    },
    {
        "text": "Literally half.",
        "start": 85.42,
        "duration": 0.9
    },
    {
        "text": "So, get a half pork loin like\nthis or a whole pork loin",
        "start": 86.32,
        "duration": 4.17
    },
    {
        "text": "and make your chops from that.",
        "start": 90.49,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, look how lean that is.",
        "start": 92.65,
        "duration": 1.893
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, we're gonna be grilling this.",
        "start": 96.92,
        "duration": 2.31
    },
    {
        "text": "So, we're gonna hit it\nwith some cooking oil.",
        "start": 99.23,
        "duration": 2.839
    },
    {
        "text": "You know I'm all about that.",
        "start": 102.069,
        "duration": 1.321
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, pork is real easy to grill.",
        "start": 103.39,
        "duration": 2.66
    },
    {
        "text": "You're just, you're\ngonna need to cook it up",
        "start": 106.05,
        "duration": 1.51
    },
    {
        "text": "to about 145 degrees Fahrenheit inside.",
        "start": 107.56,
        "duration": 3.553
    },
    {
        "text": "Here, we're throwing on some seasoning.",
        "start": 112.85,
        "duration": 1.66
    },
    {
        "text": "Use your favorite seasoning, all right?",
        "start": 114.51,
        "duration": 1.9
    },
    {
        "text": "Salt, pepper, garlic or whatever.",
        "start": 116.41,
        "duration": 2.89
    },
    {
        "text": "Get the seasoning on both sides.",
        "start": 119.3,
        "duration": 1.873
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, I told you this was\ngonna be real easy to cook.",
        "start": 122.03,
        "duration": 2.73
    },
    {
        "text": "All right, now we got our\nbig black iron pan here.",
        "start": 124.76,
        "duration": 3.353
    },
    {
        "text": "And um, we're gonna heat it up.",
        "start": 129.58,
        "duration": 2.74
    },
    {
        "text": "We're using an indirect grilling method.",
        "start": 132.32,
        "duration": 2.97
    },
    {
        "text": "On the grill, we got most of the heat",
        "start": 135.29,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "concentrated to one side",
        "start": 137.39,
        "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
        "text": "and this way we can regulate the heat.",
        "start": 138.89,
        "duration": 2.213
    },
    {
        "text": "If you've been watching us\nover the years, you know that.",
        "start": 142.29,
        "duration": 3.237
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh, man.",
        "start": 145.527,
        "duration": 1.393
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, if you've never had\nsmothered pork chops before,",
        "start": 146.92,
        "duration": 3.45
    },
    {
        "text": "you definitely gotta check it out.",
        "start": 150.37,
        "duration": 1.51
    },
    {
        "text": "All right, now we've chopped\nall the veggies we needed.",
        "start": 151.88,
        "duration": 3.7
    },
    {
        "text": "Got some onions going in into the oil.",
        "start": 155.58,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "We're gonna sear it a bit.",
        "start": 157.42,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Add some butter. It\nwill easily brown quick.",
        "start": 159.42,
        "duration": 3.083
    },
    {
        "text": "Mm, that smells good already.",
        "start": 165.325,
        "duration": 1.698
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, the USDA considers the pork",
        "start": 168.84,
        "duration": 4.33
    },
    {
        "text": "a very lean meat protein.",
        "start": 173.17,
        "duration": 2.1
    },
    {
        "text": "It takes on the flavors\nof the seasoning or",
        "start": 175.27,
        "duration": 3.35
    },
    {
        "text": "marinades, whatever you got. It's great.",
        "start": 180.32,
        "duration": 1.73
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, to that, we threw in some mushrooms",
        "start": 182.05,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": "and here we're throwing\nin some chopped garlic.",
        "start": 185.49,
        "duration": 3.873
    },
    {
        "text": "We're gonna add some more butter",
        "start": 190.44,
        "duration": 1.24
    },
    {
        "text": "to continue to brown it down.",
        "start": 191.68,
        "duration": 1.55
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, you can find out the exact",
        "start": 193.23,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "ingredients and quantities\nby going to our website.",
        "start": 194.91,
        "duration": 2.793
    },
    {
        "text": "BBQPitBoys.com.",
        "start": 199.061,
        "duration": 1.25
    },
    {
        "text": "All right, we've cooked this down.",
        "start": 201.34,
        "duration": 2.413
    },
    {
        "text": "That smells good.",
        "start": 203.753,
        "duration": 1.36
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, here we're adding at the\nlast minute, some mustard.",
        "start": 205.97,
        "duration": 3.81
    },
    {
        "text": "This'll give it a lot of flavor.",
        "start": 209.78,
        "duration": 1.95
    },
    {
        "text": "And here we've got some paprika.",
        "start": 211.73,
        "duration": 2.01
    },
    {
        "text": "It's actually smoked paprika.",
        "start": 213.74,
        "duration": 2.15
    },
    {
        "text": "And this is all pit master privilege.",
        "start": 215.89,
        "duration": 2.43
    },
    {
        "text": "This is your basis for\nyour smother, alright?",
        "start": 218.32,
        "duration": 3.316
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm gonna show how\nwe're gonna do that now.",
        "start": 221.636,
        "duration": 2.077
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, here",
        "start": 224.75,
        "duration": 1.57
    },
    {
        "text": "we have, oh I'd say about\neight cups of chicken stock.",
        "start": 226.32,
        "duration": 5.0
    },
    {
        "text": "You could use a beef stock if you want.",
        "start": 231.44,
        "duration": 1.95
    },
    {
        "text": "Need plenty of stock because we need",
        "start": 235.04,
        "duration": 3.03
    },
    {
        "text": "plenty of gravy for this smother.",
        "start": 238.07,
        "duration": 2.103
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, we're gonna simmer this a bit.",
        "start": 241.92,
        "duration": 1.75
    },
    {
        "text": "Bring all those flavors together.",
        "start": 245.58,
        "duration": 1.683
    },
    {
        "text": "And um,",
        "start": 248.39,
        "duration": 1.01
    },
    {
        "text": "we're gonna make up, make up\nsome thickening for the gravy.",
        "start": 249.4,
        "duration": 4.78
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, we're gonna use flour and\nwater, that's simple right?",
        "start": 254.18,
        "duration": 3.78
    },
    {
        "text": "You can use rice flour",
        "start": 257.96,
        "duration": 2.31
    },
    {
        "text": "or whatever kind of gravy mix you have.",
        "start": 260.27,
        "duration": 3.25
    },
    {
        "text": "We're gonna add just a\nlittle bit to the pan.",
        "start": 263.52,
        "duration": 2.25
    },
    {
        "text": "Thicken it up.",
        "start": 265.77,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh man, it smells good.",
        "start": 268.45,
        "duration": 2.33
    },
    {
        "text": "With all that garlic in there.",
        "start": 270.78,
        "duration": 2.04
    },
    {
        "text": "Mushrooms, onions.",
        "start": 272.82,
        "duration": 1.593
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 275.83,
        "duration": 1.17
    },
    {
        "text": "Bring it up to a quick simmer.",
        "start": 277.0,
        "duration": 1.593
    },
    {
        "text": "All right?",
        "start": 280.39,
        "duration": 1.427
    },
    {
        "text": "It's gonna take a few minutes.",
        "start": 281.817,
        "duration": 1.746
    },
    {
        "text": "Now.",
        "start": 285.94,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "We've got the smother\nsimmering away there.",
        "start": 288.49,
        "duration": 2.95
    },
    {
        "text": "We're gonna pull it off the direct heat.",
        "start": 291.44,
        "duration": 2.44
    },
    {
        "text": "'Cause this is where we're\ngonna sear these chops, right.",
        "start": 293.88,
        "duration": 2.69
    },
    {
        "text": "Both sides. Just briefly, all right?",
        "start": 296.57,
        "duration": 2.293
    },
    {
        "text": "We want the flavor.",
        "start": 300.0,
        "duration": 1.62
    },
    {
        "text": "Profile. The grill flavor to get on these",
        "start": 301.62,
        "duration": 2.587
    },
    {
        "text": "and you can't do those in\nthe kitchen over coals.",
        "start": 304.207,
        "duration": 2.733
    },
    {
        "text": "It only takes a few minutes.",
        "start": 308.6,
        "duration": 1.713
    },
    {
        "text": "Looks good enough to eat\nalready. Give them a flip.",
        "start": 312.78,
        "duration": 2.55
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, like I said, this'll\nbring a lot of flavor",
        "start": 318.18,
        "duration": 2.58
    },
    {
        "text": "into your smothered\ngravy right there, huh.",
        "start": 320.76,
        "duration": 2.48
    },
    {
        "text": "You'll get that flavor right in there.",
        "start": 324.251,
        "duration": 1.9
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 327.187,
        "duration": 1.633
    },
    {
        "text": "They're just about the way we want them.",
        "start": 328.82,
        "duration": 2.843
    },
    {
        "text": "They're still raw on the inside.",
        "start": 332.53,
        "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
        "text": "So, this is where we're gonna slow simmer.",
        "start": 335.01,
        "duration": 2.233
    },
    {
        "text": "In this gravy.",
        "start": 338.116,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Just like that.",
        "start": 339.896,
        "duration": 1.25
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh baby. We're gonna be\neating good tonight, Martha.",
        "start": 343.356,
        "duration": 4.333
    },
    {
        "text": "Put that pretty red\ndress of yours on, whew.",
        "start": 349.09,
        "duration": 3.073
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 353.37,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Now,",
        "start": 355.95,
        "duration": 1.07
    },
    {
        "text": "we're gonna bring it up to simmer again.",
        "start": 357.02,
        "duration": 2.41
    },
    {
        "text": "And here, we've got um,",
        "start": 359.43,
        "duration": 1.353
    },
    {
        "text": "some sprigs of thyme going in.",
        "start": 361.77,
        "duration": 3.113
    },
    {
        "text": "Simmering, we'll pull\nit off the direct heat,",
        "start": 366.24,
        "duration": 2.52
    },
    {
        "text": "kind of indirect.",
        "start": 368.76,
        "duration": 1.033
    },
    {
        "text": "Gives you plenty of control\nover the simmer, all right.",
        "start": 371.01,
        "duration": 3.15
    },
    {
        "text": "Perfect.",
        "start": 375.372,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "All right.",
        "start": 380.445,
        "duration": 1.415
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm gonna check on these chops,\nmaybe flip them, all right?",
        "start": 381.86,
        "duration": 4.572
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh, they're gonna be good.",
        "start": 386.432,
        "duration": 1.448
    },
    {
        "text": "Can you smell that? It smells good.",
        "start": 387.88,
        "duration": 2.953
    },
    {
        "text": "Few minutes to go.",
        "start": 393.23,
        "duration": 0.9
    },
    {
        "text": "And in the miracle of time,",
        "start": 395.69,
        "duration": 2.22
    },
    {
        "text": "these smothered pork chops are done.",
        "start": 397.91,
        "duration": 4.14
    },
    {
        "text": "And I say it's time to eat.",
        "start": 402.05,
        "duration": 1.553
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, you can serve these\nchops up any way you want.",
        "start": 405.37,
        "duration": 4.33
    },
    {
        "text": "We have some mashed potatoes.",
        "start": 409.7,
        "duration": 1.94
    },
    {
        "text": "We've got some corn on the cob.",
        "start": 411.64,
        "duration": 2.33
    },
    {
        "text": "We have some fresh coleslaw.",
        "start": 413.97,
        "duration": 1.953
    },
    {
        "text": "You can throw these onto\nan open-faced sandwich.",
        "start": 418.58,
        "duration": 2.503
    },
    {
        "text": "Any way you want, there's\nsome good eating at the pit.",
        "start": 422.2,
        "duration": 2.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, we have to thank the\nNational Pork Board once again",
        "start": 426.9,
        "duration": 3.87
    },
    {
        "text": "for supporting the Barbecue\nPit Boys and this video.",
        "start": 430.77,
        "duration": 3.213
    },
    {
        "text": "We appreciate your support\nand your support for",
        "start": 436.12,
        "duration": 2.33
    },
    {
        "text": "over 15 thousand Barbecue\nPit Boys chapters",
        "start": 438.45,
        "duration": 3.46
    },
    {
        "text": "in the 100 countries.",
        "start": 441.91,
        "duration": 1.928
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh man.",
        "start": 443.838,
        "duration": 1.422
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah!",
        "start": 445.26,
        "duration": 1.41
    },
    {
        "text": "Man, and you can get\nthese down at Walmart too.",
        "start": 446.67,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "So, we appreciate\nWalmart's support on this.",
        "start": 448.67,
        "duration": 3.26
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, look how thick",
        "start": 451.93,
        "duration": 1.58
    },
    {
        "text": "that gravy is",
        "start": 453.51,
        "duration": 2.34
    },
    {
        "text": "on those grilled chops.",
        "start": 455.85,
        "duration": 2.77
    },
    {
        "text": "Are you kidding me?",
        "start": 458.62,
        "duration": 1.173
    },
    {
        "text": "And of course, we do have to apologize",
        "start": 463.32,
        "duration": 2.66
    },
    {
        "text": "for eating in front of you like this.",
        "start": 465.98,
        "duration": 2.3
    },
    {
        "text": "But we call this, pit\nmaster privilege. Mm!",
        "start": 468.28,
        "duration": 2.797
    },
    {
        "text": "Good!",
        "start": 475.934,
        "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, of course, I know you're asking.",
        "start": 480.36,
        "duration": 2.21
    },
    {
        "text": "So take a look at what these\nlook like on the inside.",
        "start": 482.57,
        "duration": 3.46
    },
    {
        "text": "And remember, don't overcook\nyour pork loin, all right.",
        "start": 486.03,
        "duration": 4.08
    },
    {
        "text": "It's ready to eat",
        "start": 490.11,
        "duration": 1.32
    },
    {
        "text": "and only 145 degrees Fahrenheit internal.",
        "start": 491.43,
        "duration": 3.383
    },
    {
        "text": "So, the next time you're looking\nfor a recipe for your pit,",
        "start": 496.5,
        "duration": 3.53
    },
    {
        "text": "check out BBQPitBoys.com.",
        "start": 500.03,
        "duration": 1.863
    },
    {
        "text": "(raven crowing)",
        "start": 504.388,
        "duration": 2.667
    }
]